            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>An experimental technique for the direct observation of flux line density gradients by means of the magnetooptical Faraday effect is proposed. For the case of cylindrical Nb-specimens this method was applied for the determination of volume pinning forces.</Para>
            </Abstract>
